意，盖为世戒，非为世劝也。如诸妇多矣，而独以潘金莲、李瓶儿、春梅命名者，亦楚《〔木寿〕杌》之意也。盖金莲以*死，瓶儿以孽死，春梅以淫死，较诸妇为更惨耳。借西门庆以描画世之大净，应伯爵以描画世之小丑，诸淫妇以描画世之丑婆、净婆，令人读之汗下。盖为世戒，非为世劝也。余尝曰：读《金瓶梅》而生怜悯心者，菩萨也；生畏惧心者，君子也；生欢喜心者，小人也；生效法心者，乃禽兽耳。余友人褚孝秀偕一少年同赴歌舞之筵，衍至《霸王夜宴》，少年垂涎曰：“男儿何可不如此！”褚孝秀曰：“也只为这乌江设此一着耳。” 同座闻之，叹为有道之言。若有人识得此意，方许他读《金瓶梅》也。不然，石公几为导淫宣欲之尤矣！奉劝世人，勿为西门庆之后车，可也。";s:13:"vod_play_from";s:20:"zuidam3u8$$$subom3u8";s:15:"vod_play_server";s:7:"no$$$no";s:13:"vod_play_note";s:3:"$$$";s:12:"vod_play_url";s:636:"第01集$https://hao.zuida-youku.com/20170616/NTgheO24/index.m3u8#第02集$https://hao.zuida-youku.com/20170616/JWxkJ31X/index.m3u8#第03集$https://hao.zuida-youku.com/20170616/sBfGgRMC/index.m3u8#第04集$https://hao.zuida-youku.com/20170616/e1cgrngi/index.m3u8#第05集$https://hao.zuida-youku.com/20170616/RZ6bc9an/index.m3u8$$$第01集$https://www.183757.com/20190225/V5JcBL6w/index.m3u8#第02集$https://www.183757.com/20190225/rwcNt71j/index.m3u8#第03集$https://www.183757.com/20190225/TlVM7RXJ/index.m3u8#第04集$https://www.183757.com/20190225/HG4aBo0E/index.m3u8#第05集$https://www.183757.com/20190225/JGQh5ltS/index.m3u8";s:13:"vod_down_from";s:0:"";s:15:"vod_down_server";s:0:"";s:13:"vod_down_note";s:0:"";s:12:"vod_down_url";s:0:"";s:13:"vod_play_list";a:2:{i:1;a:9:{s:3:"sid";i:1;s:11:"player_info";a:9:{s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:4:"from";s:9:"zuidam3u8";s:4:"show";s:15:"【极速线】";s:3:"des";s:0:"";s:2:"ps";s:1:"1";s:5:"parse";s:18:"//z1.m1907.cn/?jx=";s:4:"sort";s:4:"1000";s:3:"tip";s:34:"在线播放,无需安装播放器";s:2:"id";s:9:"zuidam3u8";}s:11:"server_info";N;s:4:"from";s:9:"zuidam3u8";s:3:"url";s:329:"第01集$https://hao.zuida-youku.com/20170616/NTgheO24/index.m3u8#第02集$https://hao.zuida-youku.com/20170616/JWxkJ31X/index.m3u8#第03集$https://hao.zuida-youku.com/20170616/sBfGgRMC/index.m3u8#第04集$https://hao.zuida-youku.com/20170616/e1cgrngi/index.m3u8#第05集$https://hao.zuida-youku.com/20170616/RZ6bc9an/index.m3u8";s:6:"server";s:2:"no";s:4:"note";s:0:"";s:9:"url_count";i:5;s:4:"urls";a:5:{i:1;a:4:{s:4:"name";s:8:"第01集";s:3:"url";s:56:"https://hao.zuida-youku.com/20170616/NTgh